{
  "stem": "17337.1",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 315.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But they didn't have where to be-- where to have a meal for-- for Sabbath.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So we used to take a-- always a man for-- for our Sabbath meal.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Mhm.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, there was a lot anti-Semitism.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] Many time you were beat up during recess, you know, in the school's [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] yard, you know.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And you always-- you-- you couldn't attend together with all the other Polish kids' plays or something because they would beat you up or something.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So most of the time I was standing, like, in a corner, against a wall or something, you know.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And after recess, you went back to-- to school.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And-- and in Poland, you see, that was-- when there was religion, we had to leave, to stay in the corridors when they had religious classes, you know.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And the church was not friendly to Jews, you know, in Poland, like it is now, you know.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And we used to have religion separate, I think.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Once a month, it used to come a-- a Hebrew teacher or a religious teacher.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And we had afternoon, in school for an hour, religion classes.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, that I-- I attended after noon.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And about two or three times a-- a week, I used to go for a couple of hours to go to a cheder, yes.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well-- [SIGHS]-- I was not a good student, let's put it this way.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It didn't-- didn't go into my head.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It wasn't a-- a very religious cheder, you know.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Just we learned the main thing, you know, about-- about the religion, you know.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS]",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So, you know, I went in cheder just maybe for three, four years because then the war started, you know.",
      "word_count": 20
    }
  ],
